00:05:49.940 --> 00:05:52.420
act on our hypothesis, and test them out.

92
00:05:53.060 --> 00:05:55.780
So the question is: how can we close this gap?

93
00:05:56.230 --> 00:06:00.000
How can we fulfill this gap that is opening between the

94
00:06:00.020 --> 00:06:03.420
demand for discovery and the supply of human

