00:08:13.056 --> 00:08:13.436
steps,

131
00:08:14.636 --> 00:08:16.155
we come up with a result.

132
00:08:17.356 --> 00:08:21.316
So the research tasks are manual, slow, and very

133
00:08:21.396 --> 00:08:22.436
costly to run today.

134
00:08:23.376 --> 00:08:24.376
So the goal is

135
00:08:25.536 --> 00:08:29.516
to develop an environment in which scientists are able to do their work,

136
00:08:29.916 --> 00:08:31.296
where all these small steps

137
00:08:32.177 --> 00:08:35.917
