143
00:08:55.076 --> 00:08:58.876
First important consequence of this is that we can democratize

144
00:08:59.036 --> 00:09:00.376
expertise,

145
00:09:01.556 --> 00:09:05.016
in a sense that there are only few places in the world where we really have the

146
00:09:05.056 --> 00:09:08.936
critical mass of scientists to do the groundbreaking research.

147
00:09:10.056 --> 00:09:10.776
But with

148
00:09:12.136 --> 00:09:15.796
AI-based co-scientists, anyone in the earth gets now

149
00:09:15.816 --> 00:09:19.616
access to the critical mass of expertise to do their

150
00:09:20.736 --> 00:09:24.556
research. So wet lab scientist has access to a

151
00:09:24.636 --> 00:09:28.436
programmer, a programmer has access to a wet lab scientist.

152
00:09:29.036 --> 00:09:32.956
It also will lead to dramatic time savings because tasks

153
00:09:33.036 --> 00:09:35.576
once took months, now they can take minutes.

154
00:09:36.656 --> 00:09:40.496
And for example, drugs or therapeutics can be brought to

155
00:09:40.506 --> 00:09:41.826
market earlier.

156
00:09:42.856 --> 00:09:46.476
And what is also important is the enablement of novel

