305
00:18:46.388 --> 00:18:50.148
go and validate the work completed by the

306
00:18:50.168 --> 00:18:50.588
agent.

307
00:18:51.928 --> 00:18:55.508
So what does this mean? This means that we have basically developed

308
00:18:55.968 --> 00:18:57.028
an integrated

