01:31:51.660 --> 01:31:54.800
session, Dr. Faisal Mahmood from Harvard.

1499
01:31:54.820 --> 01:31:58.300
He's very well-known. He's maybe the godfather of

1500
01:31:58.340 --> 01:32:02.260
pathology foundation models. His team has published

