01:32:02.320 --> 01:32:06.160
several of the leading pathology foundation models that are being used by

1502
01:32:06.219 --> 01:32:09.950
teams worldwide, have been used in thousands of publications,

1503
01:32:10.440 --> 01:32:14.410
and now I'm very excited that he, I think, is also

